From July 23rd to July 27th there will be a brand new evangelism training to help you learn and practice new skills for sharing the Gospel with others. It will be taught by experienced evangelists and pastors from the area and it will take place at Langalanga Baptist Church in Kitale. Langalanga is also where the water well project will take place. The goal is to equip and encourage 30 plus local pastors and church leaders to share Christ in new ways. Please pray for a good turn

Healed of malaria, bacterial infection and kidney pain Sita’s wife told you more about the Oh family when she told about their fire the last time. Now I have a new story to tell about them. This family is from India, and have 6 children. On one Friday morning earlier this summer I got a desperate phone call from their drunk father. He started by telling me about his wife who was suffering from kidney pain. They were about to go to a hospital when I told him to bring his wife to me
